          "text": "Location: United Kingdom<p>Remote: Preferred<p>Willing to Relocate: Possibly, for a perfect role<p>Technologies: Jamf · Microsoft Intune · Microsoft Entra (Azure AD) · MCAS · Microsoft Endpoint Configuration Manager · Active Directory · Microsoft Defender for\nEndpoint · Microsoft 365<p>Résumé&#x2F;CV: <a href=\"https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.linkedin.com&#x2F;in&#x2F;gwilliamsuk&#x2F;\" rel=\"nofollow\">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.linkedin.com&#x2F;in&#x2F;gwilliamsuk&#x2F;</a><p>Email: hackernews@grayw.co.uk<p>Endpoint Management &amp; Security Engineer seeking a new adventure! I bring a wealth of experience in deploying automated endpoint solutions. From threat detection to seamless device management.<p>Writer of popular post series around automated iMac deployments now in use across many businesses and educational institutions worldwide: <a href=\"https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;GrahamWilliams-DMT&#x2F;macadmins-presentation-labdeployment\">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;GrahamWilliams-DMT&#x2F;macadmins-presentation...</a><p>While I’m well aware this is not really aimed at my specialisation, I thought I’d take a punt in case anyone needs someone like me.<p>Blog&#x2F;Newsletter: <a href=\"https:&#x2F;&#x2F;irritatedsysadmin.substack.com&#x2F;\" rel=\"nofollow\">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;irritatedsysadmin.substack.com&#x2F;</a>",
